OL,3,CFood charity says 13% of older people
OL,4,Cexperience food poverty
OL,6,FNew data shows 13% of older people
OL,7,Facross southern Scotland may be
OL,8,Fsuffering from malnutrition.
OL,10,FFood Train, a charity based in
OL,11,FDumfries, believes the research could
OL,12,Fbe "the tip of the iceberg" with
OL,13,Funreported cases of food poverty
OL,14,Fexpected to be greater among people
OL,15,Faged 65 and over.
OL,17,FThe charity which helps older people
OL,18,Fwith malnutrition, provides food
OL,19,Fdeliveries to 620 people in Dumfries
OL,20,Fand Galloway and 152 in the Scottish
OL,21,FBorders.
