OL,3,CFood charity says 13% of older people
OL,4,Cexperience food poverty
OL,6,FThe data has been released as part of
OL,7,Fa call for action during UK
OL,8,FMalnutrition Awareness Week, 11
OL,9,FNovember - 17 November 2024.
OL,11,FFood Train is calling for increased
OL,12,Finvestment in screening and
OL,13,Fpreventative community services, with
OL,14,Fthe aim of easing financial strain on
OL,15,Fthe NHS and social care.
OL,17,FThe research also found that 16% of
OL,18,Fpeople across the nation are at risk
OL,19,Fof malnutrition.
