OL,6,FJohn Bennett, a Dumfries delivery
OL,7,Fdriver volunteer, says he sees the
OL,8,Fpositive impact food drop-offs have
OL,9,Fwithin the local community.
OL,11,F"It's good to be able to help people
OL,12,Fwhen they're not able to do their own
OL,13,Fshopping," he said. "We meet lots of
OL,14,Fdifferent people.
OL,16,F"By having their shopping delivered,
OL,17,Fit means they're able to stay in their
OL,18,Fown homes for longer. They're much
OL,19,Fhappier and healthier there."
