OL,3,CFood charity says 13% of older people
OL,4,Cexperience food poverty
OL,6,FRosie McLuskie, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FFood Train, said: "The fact that 13%
OL,8,Fof older people across the Dumfries
OL,9,Fand Galloway and Scottish Borders are
OL,10,Fat risk of malnutrition is, however,
OL,11,Fextremely worrying. But the even more
OL,12,Fconcerning reality is that this number
OL,13,Fis likely to be just the tip of the
OL,14,Ficeberg.
OL,16,F"The people we have screened are those
OL,17,Fwho have accessed a service run by us,
OL,18,For one of our partners. What about the
OL,19,Fpeople who aren't using services like
OL,20,Fours and are slipping through the net?
