OL,4,Cexperience food poverty
OL,6,F"Malnourishment among older people is
OL,7,Fa hidden problem, which has a serious
OL,8,Fimpact on people's health. For their
OL,9,Fsake, we need to redouble efforts to
OL,10,Fget an accurate picture of the scale
OL,11,Fof those at risk - and those who are
OL,12,Factually malnourished and need
OL,13,Fimmediate help."
OL,15,FThe Scottish Government says it has
OL,16,Finvested #12m in providing free
OL,17,Fwelfare and debt advice services. More
OL,18,Fthan 6,000 older people have been
OL,19,Fsupported by the Citizens Advice
OL,20,FScotland Money Talk Team Service this
OL,21,Fyear.
