OL,6,FThey have provided #2.2m from their
OL,7,FEquality and Human Rights Fund to help
OL,8,Forganisations deliver projects for
OL,9,Folder people.
OL,11,FJenni Minto, Public Health Minister,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Scotland's communities
OL,13,Fexperience health, quality of life and
OL,14,Flife expectancy differently across our
OL,15,Fsociety. No one should have to
OL,16,Fcompromise on food or other
OL,17,Fessentials, and we are working to
OL,18,Fsupport older people and tackle
OL,19,Fpoverty.
