OL,3,CFood charity says 13% of older people
OL,4,Cexperience food poverty
OL,6,F"We're focused on working with
OL,7,Fpartners and taking preventative
OL,8,Faction to drive improvements in
OL,9,Fpopulation health which will increase
OL,10,Fhealthy life expectancy and reduce
OL,11,Fhealth inequalities.
OL,13,F"The main aim of our 2018 Diet and
OL,14,FHealthy Weight Delivery Plan is to
OL,15,Fmake it easier for everyone across
OL,16,FScotland to eat well and have a
OL,17,Fhealthy weight. This includes reducing
OL,18,Flevels of undernutrition.
