OL,6,F"A working group has recently
OL,7,Fdeveloped recommendations for the
OL,8,Fprevention, early detection and early
OL,9,Fintervention of malnutrition and
OL,10,Fdehydration ` the Scottish Government
OL,11,Fis considering these recommendations."
OL,13,FThe Scottish Government states the
OL,14,Fpower to make "a real difference"
OL,15,Fremains with the UK Government.
